OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will
OL,6,Fremain cloudy during the evening and
OL,7,Fthrough the night with outbreaks of
OL,8,Fheavy and perhaps thundery rain.
OL,9,FClearer, drier spells in the west
OL,10,Ftowards morning.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FCloud and heavy, showery
OL,13,Fovernight rain clearing north in the
OL,14,Fmorning. Then sunny spells and
OL,15,Fscattered showers, these heavy at
OL,16,Ftimes.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
