OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FDry
OL,6,Fand bright start Monday before cloud
OL,7,Fand outbreaks of rain through the day.
OL,8,FVariable cloud, sunny spells and
OL,9,Foccasionally heavy showers Tuesday.
OL,10,FFurther rain or showers on Wednesday.
